28:54.200 --> 28:55.960
Buddy and Bali and...

28:57.440 --> 28:58.600
And Mac.

29:00.480 --> 29:01.480
Mac?

29:05.440 --> 29:09.440
Mac did a drug deal in Bali
and it went wrong.

29:13.560 --> 29:18.480
Trot, Mac killed someone,
a young boy.

29:18.480 --> 29:21.920
He just shot him right there
in the chest in front of us.

29:23.920 --> 29:26.280
And then Buddy just paddled it out
and just...

29:26.280 --> 29:28.000
..and just left him to the sharks.

29:29.840 --> 29:31.760
Yeah, so you all can just sit here
and get rich

29:31.760 --> 29:34.120
and wait while your American profits
start rolling in,

29:34.120 --> 29:36.280
because
no-one's going to say anything.

29:36.280 --> 29:38.240
No, Shirley. Shirley, I swear.

29:38.240 --> 29:40.360
I swear,
I didn't know anything about this.

29:40.360 --> 29:41.920
Don't worry.

29:43.080 --> 29:44.920
I'm not gonna tell anyone.

29:46.520 --> 29:49.800
Your precious little company is safe,

29:49.800 --> 29:51.960
