it's totally fine.

31:10.040 --> 31:12.440
I'm telling you,
offshore production's the future.

31:12.440 --> 31:15.080
The sooner you offload
this Australian payroll,

31:15.080 --> 31:16.640
the sooner
you start to see a profit.

31:16.640 --> 31:18.480
(CLEARS THROAT)
Oh, jeez.

31:20.360 --> 31:22.560
