some warning next time?

31:25.200 --> 31:26.480
(LAUGHS)

31:26.480 --> 31:28.400
Can you hear yourself?

31:28.400 --> 31:31.520
OK, mate, why don't we give the, ah,
Dodger here a little bit of space.

31:31.520 --> 31:32.560
Hey.
Come on.

31:32.560 --> 31:34.400
Morning.

31:34.400 --> 31:35.440
So that's it?

31:35.440 --> 31:37.640
