and pay it off.

32:54.920 --> 32:56.640
How are you gonna work here
if I work here?

32:56.640 --> 32:59.560
No-one is working here!

33:01.640 --> 33:03.680
Now go on, rack off!

33:03.680 --> 33:04.920
Both of you.

33:07.800 --> 33:09.520
You know,
you should have your own place, Reg.

33:09.520 --> 33:12.320
Jesus, Dim,
just give it a rest, mate!

33:30.480 --> 33:32.240
We have to talk, Trace.

33:33.320 --> 33:34.320
OK.

33:35.320 --> 33:36.760
Let's hear it.

33:36.760 --> 33:38.000
I fucked up.

33:38.000 --> 33:39.520
Yeah, you did.

33:39.520 --> 33:42.200
Look, I didn't plan to see her,
but it happened.

33:42.200 --> 33:44.160
