33:44.160 --> 33:45.440
It's not like that.

33:47.640 --> 33:49.880
Don't act like you didn't have
a choice, Trot.

33:49.880 --> 33:52.960
Look, I know this doesn't make it
any easier to hear, but what you saw

33:52.960 --> 33:56.000
