everything and saying goodbye.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.040
Goodbye?

33:59.600 --> 34:01.640
You live in the same town, Trot.

34:02.720 --> 34:04.720
What did you think that you would do?

34:04.720 --> 34:07.960
See Sharpie at the pub
and have a drink with him?

34:07.960 --> 34:10.400
Or have them over for dinner?

34:10.400 --> 34:13.560
Watch me
try and be friendly with her?

34:13.560 --> 34:17.360
Yeah, I don't know
what I was thinking.

34:17.360 --> 34:19.760
Well, clearly
you weren't thinking about me.

34:23.440 --> 34:25.360
What do you need me to...

34:25.360 --> 34:26.360
..to do, Tracy?

34:28.000 --> 34:29.600
What do you need me to do
to make this up to you?

34:29.600 --> 34:31.440
I'll do anything.
I'll do everything.

34:31.440 --> 34:33.000
I don't think you can.

34:34.120 --> 34:35.520
It's too late, Trot.

34:40.000 --> 34:41.360
Why her?

34:43.840 --> 34:45.960
What does she have that I don't?

34:53.560 --> 34:55.960
Give me another chance, Trace.

34:55.960 --> 34:57.560
Just go.

34:59.040 --> 35:00.040
Please.

35:37.400 --> 35:40.080
What did you think
when you were fucking my girlfriend?

35:41.520 --> 35:43.120
That it didn't matter
about anyone else?

35:43.120 --> 35:44.840
We'd had a lot to drink.
It was a one-off thing.

35:44.840 --> 35:45.960
Yeah, yeah. Shut up.

35:45.960 --> 35:47.480
Mate...
I don't wanna know.

35:48.560 --> 35:52.400
Here's the thing, Trot,
we're not mates.

35:53.560 --> 35:57.520
Yeah, definitely not now,
but I don't think we ever were.

36:01.840 --> 36:05.480
You took the best thing I ever had

36:05.480 --> 36:07.200
