up against the wall.

36:10.160 --> 36:12.000
You just want everything, don't ya?

36:12.000 --> 36:13.840
Yeah, that's me.

36:13.840 --> 36:15.280
Arsehole.

36:15.280 --> 36:16.800
Take a swing.

36:16.800 --> 36:17.840
What did you say?

36:17.840 --> 36:20.400
Take a swing, Sharpie. Go on,
I'm an arsehole. I deserve it.

36:20.400 --> 36:21.640
Punch me.

36:26.800 --> 36:28.960
