that does feel kinda better.

36:44.760 --> 36:46.320
Are you alright?

36:46.320 --> 36:47.680
Yeah.

37:08.200 --> 37:09.960
Do you mind
if I start with some photos?

37:09.960 --> 37:11.120
Yeah, sure.

37:14.800 --> 37:16.080
Great.
Hey, try that.

37:16.080 --> 37:17.080
Hmm.

37:17.080 --> 37:18.760
(GIGGLES)

37:18.760 --> 37:21.040
I gotta say, this looks like
the perfect party house.

37:21.040 --> 37:23.080
Yeah. We've had a few.

37:23.080 --> 37:24.080
I bet.

37:24.080 --> 37:27.560
So is that the lifestyle
that you're trying to sell?

37:27.560 --> 37:29.640
(CAMERA CLICKS)

37:30.680 --> 37:35.000
We make shorts for surfers,
designed by surfers.

37:35.000 --> 37:37.800
You know what,
why don't we move you to the couch?

37:39.960 --> 37:41.760
We're at the beach, right?

37:41.760 --> 37:43.040
So...

37:43.040 --> 37:44.400
Yep.

37:44.400 --> 37:45.520
Put your feet up.

37:51.440 --> 37:53.120
