38:41.440 --> 38:43.960
(CAMERA CLICKS)

38:58.440 --> 39:00.080
Would you excuse me for a moment?

39:00.080 --> 39:03.000
I'll show you some of the trunks.

39:06.760 --> 39:09.080
You created LightWave?

39:09.080 --> 39:11.040
I'm selling a story.

39:11.040 --> 39:12.120
Trotter's story.

39:12.120 --> 39:14.160
Well, what does it matter?
Trotter made up half of it, anyway.

39:14.160 --> 39:15.640
We were all in Bali together.

39:15.640 --> 39:17.120
Who even is that guy?

39:17.120 --> 39:20.360
Look, I'm doing an interview
for West Coast Business News.

39:20.360 --> 39:22.360
