39:34.440 --> 39:36.920
All we have to do is stay clear-eyed

39:36.920 --> 39:39.320
and you and I
are sitting on a goldmine.

39:40.400 --> 39:41.800
Clear-eyed?

39:44.920 --> 39:47.120
What, you're telling me
you're not high right now?

39:47.120 --> 39:48.120
Come on.

39:51.040 --> 39:53.840
Here's the cash
for Trotter's licence fee.

39:53.840 --> 39:56.560
Do you want me to tell your little
reporter friend how I got that?

39:59.960 --> 40:03.920
Hey, anything you need to know
about the business, this guy,

40:03.920 --> 40:06.040
this guy right here, he's your man.

40:06.040 --> 40:07.400
Alright?

40:10.920 --> 40:12.920
Ah, trouble in paradise?

40:12.920 --> 40:14.120
Oh, no, it's all good.

40:14.120 --> 40:15.200
All good.

40:15.200 --> 40:16.680
Shall we continue?

40:16.680 --> 40:18.040
Sure.

40:18.040 --> 40:19.320
(SIGHS)

40:19.320 --> 40:21.160
Why don't you pass me those?
Yeah.

40:35.280 --> 40:36.280
Ahem.

40:37.280 --> 40:39.320
