and then he breaks my heart.

40:48.600 --> 40:50.040
Well, that's no good.

40:50.040 --> 40:52.120
No, it's not.

40:52.120 --> 40:56.200
So I made a rule that I wasn't
gonna do one-night stands anymore.

40:58.080 --> 41:00.240
You know, we were really,
really drunk.

41:00.240 --> 41:02.080
You don't have to feel bad about it.

41:03.280 --> 41:05.600
Oh, I don't regret rooting you.

41:05.600 --> 41:08.600
No, I've been reading this book
by Erica Jong, The Fear of Flying.

41:08.600 --> 41:10.440
There's this thing
that the woman does in the story,

41:10.440 --> 41:11.960
it's called a zipless...

41:16.120 --> 41:17.400
A zipless fuck.

41:18.440 --> 41:21.840
Is that, like,
sex with the clothes on or...?

41:21.840 --> 41:27.560
No. It's sorta like
sex without power or commitment.

41:27.560 --> 41:31.200
No-one asks any questions or wants
anything other than just sex.

41:31.200 --> 41:32.960
I wanna give it a try.

41:32.960 --> 41:34.400
With me?

41:34.400 --> 41:35.720
Of course with you.

41:36.800 --> 41:38.160
You in?

41:39.440 --> 41:40.600
Yeah.

41:43.120 --> 41:44.520
Glad we sorted that.

41:58.800 --> 42:00.520
What are you doing?

42:00.520 --> 42:04.240
It's a, ah, drumroll for when
you open that up and read the price.

42:05.280 --> 42:06.480
Right.

42:08.320 --> 42:11.000
